title: Cycling Horoscopes For the Week of Jan 15: The Sun and Aquarius Dance-Off
content:
Things are going to get a bit weird this week. Don’t worry, I have you covered in these latest horoscopes. I’m framing it for you all as a dance-off, as opposed to the Sun entering Aquarius. I’m 7 for 7 in dance-off’s at weddings around the world. Listen up moon-lovers! Aries You ready to dance? … Continued
